Kotu ta banka wuta a yayin zanga-zanga a California
Oakland, Ca. - Masu zanga-zanga a California sun cinnawa wata kotu wuta, inda suka lalata ofishin 'yan sanda tare da farma jami'an 'yan sanda bayan da zanga-zangar lumana ta tsananta da yammacin ranar Asabar, in ji 'yan sandan Oakland.
Masu zanga zangar sun farfasa tagogi, da fesa fentin gwal, da harba abubuwan tartsatsin wuta da kuma nuna lasifikoki ga jami'ai, a cewar wani ma'aikaci a Oakland a shafinsa na Twitter.
Tweets da dama sun yi kira da a zauna lafiya kuma sun nemi masu tsare-tsare da su "taimaka mana wajen samar da wurare masu hadari da kuma wurare masu hadari ga masu zanga-zanga".
Zanga-zangar ta soma ne da yammacin ranar Asabar tare da kungiyoyi irin su "Wall of Moms", kama daga wata kungiya da ta kafu a Portland da ke Oregon, yayin da masu zanga-zangar suka fusata tare da tura jami'an Amurka zuwa wannan birni domin tsare wata kotun tarayya.
Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya aike da jami'an tsaro na tarayya domin matsa kaimi kan zanga-zangar da ta auku ba kakkautawa tun bayan mutuwar George Floyd a Minneapolis a ranar 25 ga watan Mayu.
Zanga-zangar da aka yi a Oakland an fara ta ne cikin lumana, amma ta rikide ta koma tashin hankali daga baya zuwa dare.
'Yan sanda sun sanar da yin "taro ba bisa ka'ida ba" da misalin karfe 11: 30 na dare kuma jami'ai sun nemi jama'a da su watse.
Wutar dajin ta tashi ne a wata babbar kotu da ke Alameda County Superior Courthouse kuma an dauke ta bayan wani dan lokaci, kamar yadda kafafen yada labarai suka ruwaito.
'Yan sanda sun ce masu zanga-zangar a wani lokaci suna "farfasa tagogi suna kuma rera wakokin nuna wariyar launin fata ga mazauna wurin".
