An Gabatar Da Tsauraran Matakan Tsaro a Wajen Taron Amurka a Chengdu, China
An dai tsaurara matakan tsaro a kofar ofishin jakadancin Amurka da ke birnin Chengdu na kasar China a yau Lahadi, yayin da ma'aikatan Amurkan ke shirin barin wurin.
An ga wasu manyan motoci masu motsi guda uku sun shiga harabar ginin, yayin da 'yan sanda marasa matsuguni da shinge suka hade bangarorin titin biyu, wadanda aka lullube su da shingayen karfe.
Editan jaridar Global Times ta kasar Sin ya tabattar da cewa, an baiwa ofishin jakadancin Amurka dake birnin Chengdu wa'adin sa'o'i 72 da ya rufe, ko kuma har zuwa karfe 10 na safe (0200GMT) Litinin 27 ga watan Yuli.
Kasar Sin ta yi zargin cewa, wasu ma'aikata da ke shawarwarin Chengdu suna "gudanar da ayyuka ba tare da la'akari da asalinsu ba".
Ba tare da bayar da wani cikakken bayani ba, mai magana da yawun ma'aikatar harkokin wajen kasar Sin, Wang Wenbin ya ce, irin wannan aiki ya yi katsalandan a harkokin kasar Sin, ya kuma cutar da muradun tsaron ta.
A ranar Juma'a ne aka bayar da umarnin kasar Sin na rufe shawarwarin a birnin Chengdu, a wani mataki na ramuwar gayya kan umarnin da Amurka ta bayar na rufe ofishin jakadancin kasar Sin dake birnin Houston na jihar Texas.
Washington ta umarci China da ta rufe ofishin Houston "don kare martabar ilimin Amurka da kuma bayanan sirri na Amurkawa".
Yayin da rufe ofishin jakadancin kasar Sin da ke Houston ya soma aiki a ranar Juma'a, an ga wasu gungun mutane da suka bayyana cewa jami'an Amurka ne sun yi raga-raga da wurin ta kofar baya.
Wang ya ce, a ranar Asabar, hakan ya sabawa yarjejeniyoyin kasa da kasa da na shiyya-shiyya, kuma kasar Sin za ta mayar da martani, ba tare da ta fayyace yadda za a yi ba.
Rufewar titinan ya kara zafafa takaddamar da ke tsakanin kasashen biyu kan batutuwan da suka jibanci cinikayya da masana'antu da kuma kare hakkin bil adama.
Un ta ce dubban masu tsatstsauran ra'ayi ne a Afghanistan
Wani rahoto na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ya ce sama da 'yan Pakistan 6,000 ne ke boye a Afghanistan, mafi yawansu na hannun kungiyar Taliban ta Pakistan da aka dorawa alhakin kai wa sojin Pakistan da fararen hula hari.
A rahoton da ta fitar a wannan makon ta ce kungiyar da ake kira Tehreek-e-Taliban (TTP), ta na da alaka da kungiyar IS mai da'awar kafa daular musulunci a Afghanistan.
Wasu daga cikin 'ya 'yan kungiyar ta TTP har sun shiga cikin kungiyar ta IS wacce ke da hedikwatarta a gabashin Afghanistan.
Gwamnatin Afganistan ba ta mayar da martani ba a ranar Lahadi kan buƙatun da kamfanin dillancin labaran Associated Press ya yi mata na neman afuwa.
Rahoton ya ce kungiyar IS a Afghanistan wacce aka fi sani da IS a lardin Khorasan, ta sha da kyar daga jami'an tsaron Afganistan da kuma dakarun Amurka da na NATO, har ma a wasu lokutan kungiyar Taliban ta Afganistan.
Tawagar masu sa ido kan harkokin nazari da takunkumi ta Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ce ta shirya rahoton, inda ta ke bin diddigin kungiyoyin ta'addanci a duniya.
Rahoton ya kiyasta cewa membobin kungiyar IS a Afghanistan sun kai 2,200, kuma yayin da aka fatattaki shugabanninta, har yanzu kungiyar IS na kirga shugabanninta wani dan asalin kasar Syria Abu Said Mohammad al-Khorasani.
Rahoton ya kuma ce tawagar masu sa idon ta samu bayanan da ke cewa wasu manyan kwamandojin IS biyu, Abu Qutaibah da Abu Hajar al-Iraqi, sun iso Afghanistan daga Gabas ta Tsakiya a baya-bayan nan.
"Duk da cewa a yankuna koma baya, (gwamnatin Musulunci) ta kasance mai iya kai hare-hare masu yawan gaske a sassa daban-daban na kasar, ciki har da birnin Kabul.
Hakan kuma na nufin janyo hankalin mayakan Taliban da ke adawa da yarjejeniyar da Amurka ", a cewar rahoton, yana nufin yarjejeniyar zaman lafiya da Amurka ta sanya wa hannu da Taliban a watan Fabarairu.
An ƙulla wannan yarjejeniyar ce domin baiwa Amurka damar kawo ƙarshen ta'asar da ta kwashe shekaru 19 ta na yi a Afghanistan, kuma ta na kira ga Taliban da ta ba ta tabbacin cewa ƙungiyoyin ta'addanci ba za su yi amfani da yankinta ba.
Ana kuma sa ran yarjejeniyar za ta ba da tabbacin shigar 'yan Taliban cikin yakin da ake da IS baki daya.
Bangare na biyu kuma watakila mafi mahimmanci a cikin yarjejeniyar ya bukaci tattaunawa tsakanin 'yan Taliban da shugabanin siyasar Kabul.
Da maraicen Asabar, Ma'aikatar Harkokin Wajen Amurka ta bayar da sanarwar cewa, babban jami'inta na wanzar da zaman lafiya Zalmay Khalilzad ya sake kutsawa ta cikin yankin yana mai neman tsallake fara wadannan shawarwari, wadanda aka dade ana dagawa yayin da bangarorin biyu ke matsi kan shirin sakin fursunoni.
Yarjejeniyar da ke samun goyon bayan Amirka ta bukaci gwamnatin Afganistan da ta saki fursunoni 'yan Taliban 5,000 sannan kungiyar Taliban ta 'yantar da ma'aikatan gwamnati da na soji 1,000 a matsayin abinda ta kira kyakkyawar manufa gabanin tattaunawa.
Har ya zuwa yanzu gwamnati ta ki sakin fursunoni 'yan Taliban kusan 600 da ta kira masu aikata manyan laifuka kuma ta yi tayin ba su wasu hanyoyi na kyauta.
'Yan Taliban dai sun ki amincewa.
"Jam'iyyun sun fi kusa da fara tattaunawar shige-da-fice a Afganistan, muhimmin mataki na gaba da zai kawo karshen yakin da Afghanistan ta kwashe shekaru 4 ta na yi", a cewar sanarwar da Ma'aikatar Harkokin Wajen Amurka ta fitar.
"Duk da cewa an samu gagarumin ci gaba a kan mu'amilla da fursunoni, amma batun na bukatar karin kokari wajen ganin an magance matsalar".
Mai magana da yawun 'yan siyasa na kungiyar Taliban a farkon makon nan ya ce a shirye ya ke ya tattauna da shugabannin siyasa na birnin Kabul bayan da aka kammala hutun Sallar Idi al-Adha a karshen watan nan, wanda hakan zai ba da damar sakin fursunonin.
Wani babban abin damuwa ga Pakistan shi ne kasancewar Afghanistan na masu tada kayar baya, musamman wadanda ke da alaka da TTP ko Jamaat-ul-Ahrar ko Lashkar-e-Islam, da kuma wadanda ke tare da rundunar 'yantar da yankin Baluchistan, wadanda suka dauki alhakin kai hare-hare masu martaba a wannan wata a lardin Sindh da ke kudu maso yammacin Lardin Baluchistan.
An kashe dakarun sojin Pakistan da dama a wannan watan a kudu maso yammacin lardin Baluchistan a yakin da suke da masu tayar da kayar baya.
Kungiyar TTP ta dauki alhakin daya daga cikin hare-haren kunar bakin waken da aka kai a Pakistan a shekarar 2014, lokacin da aka kai hari a wata makarantar sojojin Pakistan aka kuma kashe 140.
Yawancinsu dalibai ne, wasu kuma shekarunsu ba su kai 5 ba.
"Adadin mayakan 'yan ta'addan kasashen waje 'yan asalin Pakistan da ke Afghanistan, da ke zama barazana ga kasashen biyu, an kiyasta yawansu a tsakanin 6,000 zuwa 6,500, yawancinsu suna da TTP", a cewar rahoton.
Babban bankin Birtaniya HSBC ya musanta "kafa tarko" ga kamfanin Huawei na China a binciken da Amurka ta ke yi - RT labaran kasuwanci
HSBC mai hedikwata a bankin sana'o'i da ke da hedikwata a birnin London-HSBC ya je shafinsa na sada zumunta ya na mai cewa ba haka ba ne, kamar yadda kafofin yada labaran China su ka yi ikirari, "kirkirar shaidu" a kan Huawei, wanda har ya kai ga kama babban jami'in kula da harkokin kudi na kamfanin a Canada.
A cikin wani sakon ba-zata da ta sa a shafinta na WeChat, mai bayar da lamunin ya ce, abinda ta aikata bai jawo binciken da Amurka ta ke yi kan babban mai samar da na'urorin sadarwa na zamani a duniya ba, yayin da binciken da Huawei ta ke yi na zargin karya takunkumin da Amurka ta kakabawa Iran ya fara aiki gadan-gadan kafin shigar bankin a karshen shekarar 2016.
"HSBC ba ta nuna kiyayya ga Huawei kuma ba ta" firgita "Huawei ba", in ji bankin a ranar Asabar, yana mai karawa da cewa ba zai taba gurbata duk wasu abubuwa game da abokan huldarta ba.
"Dangane da bukatar DOJ na Amurka [Ma'aikatar Shari'a ta Amurka] na neman bayanai, Kungiyar HSBC ce kawai ta gabatar da gaskiyar manufar.
HSBC ba ta "ƙiƙiro" shaida ko "ɓoye" gaskiya ba".
Har ila yau a shafin rt.com Matakin da Burtaniya ta dauka na hana kamfanin Huawei daga hanyar sadarwar 5G ya nuna Amurka ta yi kama-karya kan manufofin harkokin wajen Biritaniya - George Gkyay ga kamfanin Boom Bust
An toshe sakon a dandalin tare da bayanin cewa "ya sabawa ka'idoji" kuma ba a samunsa a yanzu.
Wannan sanarwa na zuwa ne jim kadan bayan da wasu kafofin yada labarai da yawa na China, ciki har da jaridun da ke da nasaba da wannan, suka zargi HSBC da "hada baki" da Washington don kafa wa Huawei tarko.
Kamfanin ya kasance a sahun gaba a wata badakalar diflomasiyya ta sama da shekara daya da rabi tun bayan da aka kama Huawei CFO Meng Wanzhou a watan Disambar shekarar 2018 a Canada a bisa sammacin kama shi daga Amurka.
Meng na fuskantar tuhume-tuhume na zamba kan zargin amfani da wani kamfanin Shell wajen kakabawa Iran takunkumi da kuma zargin yin karya ga bankuna game da alakar da ke tsakanin Huawei da kamfanin Skycom na Iran.
Bisa sabbin shaidun da jaridar Global Times ta bayar, an ce, HSBC yana sane da dangantakar kamfanin kasar Sin da Skycom.
Bankin ya bayar da rahoton cewa, ya gwammace ya yi "tattaki" da gwamnatin Amurka don tserewa hukunci mai tsanani a shekarar 2012, a lokacin da bankin ya shigar da karar halatta kudin haram da kuma takunkumin karya tattalin arziki, ciki har da takurawa Iran.
An umarce ta a lokacin da ta biya kusan dala biliyan 1.9 kudin fensho da kuma hana duk wata barna makamanciyar wannan.
"Shaidun sun nuna cewa HSBC ta fahimci wannan alakar, amma da gangan ta sayar da takardun kasuwancinta na sirri ga bangaren Amurka domin gwamnatin Amurka ta sa ido kan yadda bankin na Birtaniya ya nuna halin ko in kula, kuma ba za ta hukunta shi ba a karkashin yarjejeniyar tabbatar da tsaro ta shekarar 2012", a cewar jaridar a daya daga cikin labaran da ta bayar kan batun.
A cikin wani kashedi da ta yi, jaridar Beijing-controlled ta kara da cewa mai bayar da bashin, idan aka tabbatar da cewa yana da laifi a cikin wannan "tattaki", zai iya fuskantar "hukunci mai tsanani" a China, daya daga cikin manyan kasuwanni na HSBC.
Wannan dai ba shi ne karon farko da mashahurin bankin ke cin wuta ba a 'yan makonnin da suka gabata.
A watan da ya gabata, an ragargaji HSBC saboda goyon bayan sabuwar dokar tsaron kasa ga Hong Kong, birnin da aka fara kasuwancinsa kuma wanda ya kai sama da rabin ribarsa.
Bankin ya fuskanci kakkausar suka daga bangarorin biyu - daga kasashen Yamma, a inda Sakataren Harkokin Wajen Amurka Mike Pompeo ya kira jimillar "kamfanoni kowtow", da kuma Gabas ta Tsakiya, tare da bayar da rahoton cewa bangaren China na cewa, tallafinta "na hakika ne".
Ma'aikatan kashe gobara sun samu sukunin kashe gobara a makociyar gundumar Lassen
Ma'aikatan kashe gobara na samun galaba a kan wasu gobarar daji biyu da ta kone fiye da eka 30,000 a karamar hukumar Lassen, arewa maso gabashin Sakkwato.
Wutar dajin ta Zinariya wacce ta soma kudu da Adin, tana dauke da kashi 40% yayin da ta ke ci gaba da yin barazana ga gidaje da matsugunai da kuma ayyukan noma da dabbobi da katako, a cewar jami'an kashe gobara na Cal a wata sabuwa ranar Asabar da safe.
Bayan kone-kone na tsawon kwanaki hudu, wutar ta yi taho-mu-gama ta hanyar hekta 21,000, ta kuma lalata gidaje bakwai tare da aika jami'an kashe gobara biyu zuwa asibiti.
Ba dare ba rana, ma'aikatan kashe gobara sun yi amfani da yanayi mai wuya wajen ginawa da kuma karfafa layukan kula da su.
Amma ana sa ran samun iska mai karfi da kuma zafi mai zafi a ranar Asabar.
Yammacin Susanville, wata karamar gobara da aka fi sani da wutar Hog ta hallaka gine-gine biyu tare da cinye kimanin eka 10,000.
Wutar ta lafa cikin dare a yayin da ma'aikatan kashe gobara ke aikin kashe gobara tare da karfafa layukan kula da su, a cewar ma'aikatar kula da gandun dazuka da kare gobara ta California.
Da sanyin safiyar Asabar ne aka samu kashi 45% kuma an kona su tsawon kwanaki shida.
A lokacin zafi na rana, da yanayin zafi da ke sama da digiri 90 a yankin Susanville, hayaki mai sa hawaye na cikin hadarin tashi.
Yayin da ake barin wasu mazauna unguwanninsu su koma gidajensu, wasu wuraren a duka wuraren da ke ci da wuta na ci gaba da kasancewa a karkashin umarnin da aka bayar na tantancewa.
An sallami ma'aikatan kashe gobara biyu da suka samu raunuka a gobarar Zinare daga asibiti.
Aljeriya: Mutuwar Mahmoud Guemama - Aljeriya Ta Rasa Marasa Galihu, In Ji Shugaba Tebboune.
Shugaban kasar Jamhuriyar Algiers, Abdelmadjid Tebboune, ya aike da sakon ta'aziyya ga 'yan majalisar dokokin kasar (APN), Mujahed Mahmoud Guemama, wanda ya mutu a ranar Juma'a, inda ya ce Aljeriya "ta yi rashin uban kasa, kuma madugun da ya aikata abubuwan da suka shafi al'ummarsa da kuma al'ummarsa".
Aljeriya ta yi rashi a yau, sakamakon mutuwar Mujahed Mahmoud Guemama, dan kishin kasa kuma madugun da ya aikata abubuwan da suka shafi al'ummarsa da kuma al'ummarsa, mutumin da bai taba yin kasa a gwiwa ba, wanda kuma niyyarsa ta ci gaba da wanzuwa tun daga lokacin da ya dauki makamai, tare da 'yan uwansa Mujahedeen masu inganci, har zuwa numfashinsa na karshe a wannan rana ta bakin ciki da sai mun yi murabus da kanmu da nufin Allah kawai ", Shugaba Tebboune ya rubuta a sakonsa na ta'aziyya.
"Marigayi Mahmoud Guemama, tsira da amincin Allah su tabbata a gare shi, na daga cikin tsare-tsare na musamman na amintattun masu kishin kasa da suka sadaukar da kansu domin kasarsu", a cewar shugaban kasar ta Jamhuriyar.
"Marigayin ya sadaukar da rayuwarsa wajen 'yantar da Aljeriya daga azabtarwar mulkin mallaka na babu gaira babu dalili, ta hanyar shiga cikin sahun juyin juya hali a Firayi Ministan rayuwa a shekarar 1960 a sansanin horar da Tahart na tarihi wilaya VI".
Shugaba Tebboune ya ce, "Marigayi Shugaban kasa sananne ne ga kowa saboda tabbatar da madafun iko da kuma sadaukarwar da ya yi wajen ankarar da jama'a irin kyakkyawar alkiblar da ke tattare da hadin kan kasar Aljeriya".
"A kudu mai nisa, marigayi Mahmoud Guemama yana jin dadin zama mashahuri a matsayinsa na mai shiga tsakani, yana mai shiga tsakani domin sulhunta 'yan uwa a kasa guda a duk lokacin da aka kintsa wutar sabani", a cewar shugaban kasar a sakon nasa.
"Duk wadannan halaye da dabi'u sun sa marigayi Mahmoud Guemama ya samu girmamawa da amincewar mutanen Tamanrasset wadanda suka zabe shi ya wakilce su a majalisar wakilan jama'ar kasar (APN) har na tsawon wa'adi da dama, a lokacin yana jakada kuma mai kare damarmakin yankin da muradun al'ummarta, har ma da wakili kuma kakakin dukkan 'yan Aljeriya", a cewar shugaban kasar ta Jamhuriyar.
"Duk wasu kalamai na ta'aziyya ba za su isa su jinjina ga mujahed Mahmoud Guemama ba, tsira da amincin Allah su tabbata a gare shi.
Yana barin mu a yau a daidai lokacin da Aljeriya ta bukace shi ", in ji shugaban kasar.
"Ina addu'ar Allah Madaukakin Sarki da ya kewaye marigayin da rahamarSa Mai Tsarki, ya tarbe shi a cikin aljanna mai girman gaske tare da shuhadaa da kuma budurwa.
Haka kuma ina addu'ar Allah ya karawa iyalansa da masoyansa hakuri da ta'aziyya... babu wani karfi ko iko sai na Allah ", Shugaban Jamhuriyar ya kammala.
Zanga-zangar Seattle: Gobara Da Pepper Sun Fadi Yayin Tsawon Watan Maris A Cikin Birnin
Seattle - Bayan shafe makonni ana kazamin rikici tsakanin masu zanga-zanga da hukumomin tarayya a Portland, Ore., jama'a kimanin 2,000 ne suka yi dandazo a Seattle a ranar Asabar, suna bi ta kan tituna suna arangama da 'yan sanda.
'Yan sanda uku sun ji raunuka, ciki har da wanda aka kwantar a asibiti sakamakon raunin da ya samu a kafa sakamakon fashewar wani abu, an kuma kama masu zanga-zanga 16 tun da sanyin yamma, in ji 'yan sanda.
Dauke da alamu kamar su "Feds Go Home" da kuma ihu na cewa "Babu adalci, babu zaman lafiya", masu zanga-zangar sun tsaya a wurin wata cibiyar tsare matasa da za a tsare nan gaba, sun kuma cinnawa gine-ginen da ke wurin wuta.
Wasu sun farfasa tagogin kasuwannin da ke kusa da wurin.
'Yan sandan sun yi taho mu gama da jama'ar ne a unguwar Capitol Hill, inda suka yi ta jifansu da kulake da kuma barkonon tsohuwa kafin su soma kai mutane gidan yari.
Bipasha Mukherjee 'yar shekara 52 'yar asalin Kirkland, Wash. Ta ce ta soma zanga-zanga a kan tituna ne tun a watan Mayu kuma ta ce abin damuwa ne a gare ta ganin irin wadannan dabaru na zalunci da 'yan sanda ke yi.
"Wannan ba ita ce kasar da na yi gudun hijira ba", a cewar Misisi Mukherjee, wacce ta zo daga Indiya fiye da shekara 30 da suka wuce.
"Ji mu ke yi kamar mu na saurin zama jiha mai saurin fushi da kuma jihar ƴan sanda"
Michaud Savage na Seattle ya ce zanga-zangar ta samo asali ne daga hukumomin yankin da kuma tura jami'an tsaro na tarayya wadanda suka yi wata zanga-zangar adawa da wata zanga-zanga da aka dade ana yi a Portland.
Mista Savage ya ce dokar ta bacin da aka kafa a Portland, wacce ta kunshi amfani da hayaki mai sa hawaye da kuma taron jama'a, na da hatsari kuma bai dace ba.
Mista Savage ya ce yayin da ya ke wanke idanunsa daga barkonon tsohuwa da kuma reno wani rauni a hannunsa daga wata 'yar hayaki mai sa hawaye.
Mutuwar George Floyd a hannun 'yan sanda a Minneapolis a watan Mayu ya jahilci zanga-zangar da ta jawo miliyoyin jama'a fitowa kan tituna a birane da dama, amma waɗannan zanga-zangar sun wanzu a yawancin birane.
Seattle da Portland dai, sun ga yadda zanga-zangar ta tsawaita.
Masu zanga-zanga a Seattle a wani lokaci sun auka wa wasu unguwanni da dama na Capitol Hill tare da ayyana wani yanki mai cin gashin kansa.
Bayan wasu jerin harbe-harbe da aka yi a wajen ne ya sa 'yan sanda suka killace yankin, zanga-zangar ta kau.
Portland kuma, ta cigaba da zanga-zanga, tare da yin wasu jerin zanga-zanga a kusa da gine-ginen gwamanatin tarayya da ke birnin.
Bayan da shugaba Trump ya bayar da umarnin kare mutum-mutumi da dukiyoyin gwamnatin tarayya, ma'aikatar tsaron cikin gida ta tura tawagogin 'yan dabara zuwa birnin, inda suka fara wasu jerin arangama da suka yi sanadiyyar raunata masu zanga-zanga, da binciken kwakwaf da kuma kiraye-kiraye daga shugabannin yankin na jami'an tsaro na tarayya da su bar wurin.
Jama'ar da ke zanga-zanga a wannan birni sun kutsa cikin dubban jama'a, kuma ana ci gaba da zanga-zanga a wajen.
A wannan makon, jami'an tsaro na tarayya sun tura wata tawaga ta dabara zuwa Seattle, kuma masu zanga-zangar sun ambaci wannan ci gaban a matsayin dalilin daya sa aka gudanar da zanga-zangar ta ranar Asabar.
Yayin da zanga-zangar ta Portland ta kasance a cikin gari, zanga-zangar da aka yi a ranar Asabar ta zagaya yankunan da ke gabas da tsakiyar garin, inda nan ne babbar kotun tarayya ta birnin.
