Jurupa VALLEY (CBSLA) - Wata wutar daji ta tashi a ranar Asabar da rana a kwarin Jurupa, lamarin da ya kai ga mayar da martani ga ma'aikatan kashe gobara sama da 200.
An bayar da rahoton tashin gobarar ta Karen ne bayan karfe 3 na yamma a kan titin Sierra Avenue da kuma Karen Lane.
Wutar dajin ta karu daga kimanin eka 5-10 zuwa wajen eka 250 ya zuwa karfe 8 na dare.
A karshe binciken da aka yi ya nuna cewa kashi 50% ne da kuma ma'aikatan kashe gobara 225 daga ma'aikatar kashe gobara ta Cal, da ma'aikatar kashe gobara ta gundumar Riverside, da ma'aikatar kashe gobara ta birnin Corona, da kuma hukumar kashe gobara ta gundumar San Bernardino suna kan aikin kashe gobarar.
An dakatar da ci gaba da barin wuta, amma ana sa ran albarkatu za su kasance ba dare ba rana domin sa ido kan yanayi.
