'Yar damben UFC Correia ta samu kubuta bayan da ta juya baya ga abokiyar hamayyarta da ta yi kuskuren tunanin zagaye na biyu (VIDEO) - RT Sport News
Bethe Correia 'yar kasar Brazil mai rike da kambin bantamweight 'yar asalin kasar UFC ce, amma ta yi kuskuren mayar da ita abokiyar karawarta Pannie Kianzad, ta kuma yi kuskuren tunanin cewa zagayen ya kare a fafatawar da suka yi a tsibirin Fight Island, kuma ta samu tagomashi sakamakon hakan.
Zuwa karshen stanza na farko na karawarsu a katin karkashin kasa a Abu Dhabi, Correia 'yar shekara 37n ta bayyana cewa ta yi kuskuren gargadi na 10 na ainihin karshen zagaye, inda ta kai gaisuwar ban girma kafin ta juya baya ga Kianzad ta kuma kama hanyarta ta komawa kusurwa.
'Yar damben 'yar kasar Sweden da aka kamo ba tare da jinkiri ba, ta dagawa abokiyar adawarta hannu da dama kafin ta bi diddigin jerin gwanon da aka yi don mayar da Correia keji.
A lokacinda ya bayyana cikin hadari, dan Brazil sai ya sake samun iko ya tunkari barazanar ya kuma mara wa Kianzad baya kafin a kira ainihin karshen zagayen.
"Me ya faru a wurin? Toh maganata", an ji kungiyar sharhin a ESPN + tana furuci.
Wannan dai wani bangare ne na wani dare mai cike da takaici ga tsohuwar mai kalubalantar kambin bantamweight Correia, wacce ta sauka daga karagar mulki sakamakon rashin nasarar da ta yi wanda shi ne rashin nasararta ta uku a wasanninta hudu na octagon da suka wuce, ta kuma bar tarihin da ta kafa gaba daya a 11-5, da canjaras daya.
Ga Kianzad haifaffiyar kasar Iran, 'yar shekara 28, nasara ce ta biyu a juya bayan nasarar da ta samu a kan Jessica-Rose Clark a gasar damben UFC da aka yi a Moscow a cikin watan Nuwamba.
Yanzu Kianzad ita ce ta 13-5 gaba daya da kuma 2-1 a gasar damben UFC, kamar yadda matar da aka fi sani da 'Banzai' ta ke da niyyar daga martabar 135lbs.
A wani wuri kuma a daren, Robert Whittaker dan kasar Australia ya fitar da Darren Till na Ingila a gasar matsakaita ajin matsakaita, yayin da dan asalin kasar Russia, Khamzat Chimaev ya kafa tarihi na lashe fadan na biyu a cikin kwanaki 10 a tsibirin Fight Island, wanda shi ne mafi gajeren lokaci da aka taba yi tsakanin nasarorin da aka samu a gasar damben zamani na UFC.
Watford ta fice daga gasar firimiya yayin da Aubameyang ya godewa Arsenal
