Gadar Sarkar Tarayyar Scotland-Ingila ta cika shekara 200 da haihuwa
Wata gada da ta hade Scotland da Ingila ta juya shekara 200 gabanin a yi mata gyaran fuska na £10m.
Gadar Union Chain Bridge ta tsallaka Kogin Tweed daga Fishwick da ke kan iyakokin Scotland zuwa Horncliffe a Northumberland.
A lokacin da aka bude ta a shekarar 1820, ita ce gada mafi tsawo da aka taba yi na dakatar da baƙin ƙarfe a duniya da tsawon kafa 449ft (137m).
Kuma ita ce gadar farko ta ababen hawa irinta a Burtaniya.
Wani jami'in sojin ruwa na Ingilishi Capt Samuel Brown ne ya tsara wannan gada.
Ya yi facaka da kuma samar da kujerun ƙarfe da aka aikata bayan rashin jiragen ruwa na Royal Naval wanda ya karye daga igiyoyi ya shafe shi.
Abokan gadar Union Chain Bridge da kuma Institution of Civil Engineers (Ice) na kasar Scotland sun yi ta nuna alamar tsallakawa ta keke-da-keke.
Robert Hunter, na daga cikin abokan kungiyar, ya na mai cewa: "Hakika wannan daya ne daga cikin gadoji masu tarihi a duniya, kuma abin sha'awa a fannin injiniya.
"Mun shirya bukukuwa da dama domin murnar zagayowar wannan rana, amma abin takaici sai aka dage.
"Duk da haka, gaskiyar cewa ba da daɗewa ba za a fara aiki a kan gyaran £10m shine mafi kyawun ranar haihuwar da za a iya samu kuma zai tabbatar da cewa tsararraki masu zuwa za su iya jin daɗin gadar a duk tsawon lokacin da aka raba ta".
Daraktar kankara a Scotland Hannatu Smith ta bayyana gadar a matsayin "wani bangare na gadon aikin injiniya a yankin Scotland".
Ta ce: "Mun san cewa duniya sananniya ce kuma dama aiki ne da ba da dadewa ba za a fara gyaransa".
Bullar cutar salmonella ta yi ajalin mutane 212 a jihohi 23
Ranar 25 ga watan Yuli (UPI) - Cibiyar kula da yaduwar cututtuka da dakile su na binciken barkewar annobar cutar salmonella da ta yi ajalin mutane 212 a jihohi 23.
A wata sanarwar manema labarai da hukumar ta CDC ta fitar a ranar Juma'a ta ruwaito cewa mutum 87 ne suka kamu da rashin lafiya tun bayan sabuntawarta ta karshe kan bullar cutar ranar Talata.
Hukumar ta ce mutane sun fara nuna alamun kamuwa da cutar da ke da nasaba da nau'in salmonella, wanda zai iya daukar makonni biyu zuwa hudu kafin ya bayyana alamomin cutar, tsakanin 19 ga watan Yuni zuwa 11 ga watan Yuli.
Mutane talatin da daya ne aka kwantar a asibiti tun lokacin da aka soma samun bullar cutar, sai dai ba a samu rahoton wadanda suka jikkata ba.
A cewar hukumar ta CDC, kawo yanzu ba a gano takamaiman tushen nau'in salmonella ba.
Ba ta bayar da wata shawara kan cin abinci ko shan wasu kayan marmari ba, ko kuma masu sayar da kayan marmari da ka iya sayar da gurbataccen kayan marmari.
Oregon ce ta fi yawan wadanda suka kamu da cutar salmonella, inda take da mutum 51 da suka kamu, yayin da Utah ke biye mata baya da mutum 40 da aka bayar da rahoton sun kamu da cutar.
