Tun da fari a yau, ministan tsaro Rajnath Singh, da karamin ministansa Shripad Naik, da babban hafsan hafsoshin tsaro Janar Bipin Rawat, da babban hafsan hafsoshin soja Janar M Naravane, da babban hafsan hafsoshin sojin sama R K S Bhadauria da kuma babban hafsan sojin ruwa Admiral Karambir Singh su ma sun kai ziyarar ta'aziyya ga Amar Jawan Jyoti a bikin tunawa da yakin kasa.
