Sai dai kuma, wata kuri'ar jin ra'ayin jama'a da aka yi a baya-bayan nan, ta saka West a kashi biyu cikin dari a kasa, wuyansa da kuma wuyansa tare da Jo Jorgensen na Jam'iyyar Libertarian da kuma wani batu da ke gaban Howie Hawkins na Jam'iyyar Green Party.
